# Monorepo root — used when compose build.context is "." (comDash, apiGate, etc.)
# Without this, "transferring context" sends node_modules, .next, and docs (often 500MB–1GB+).

.git
**/.git
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/out
**/coverage
**/.turbo
**/.cache
**/cypress
**/.pytest_cache
**/__pycache__
*.log
*.md
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Large reference trees — keep Aurora template for comDash webpack aliases (see comDash/next.config.js).
# comDash/docs/aurora is required at build time; other docs can be excluded if added back as specific paths.
